      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a vehicle to get you from A to B with a little TLC? This car has definitely seen some miles and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, but it's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast to bring it back to life! It\u2019s priced to sell and ready for someone who isn't afraid of a little hard work.",
