      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an uncompromising level of preservation both aesthetically and mechanically. Every surface reflects a history of meticulous stewardship, offering the discerning collector a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example. Professional inspections are welcomed to verify its flawless state and investment-grade quality.",
